additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Causes serious eye damage. May cause an allergic skin reaction when undiluted. Keep out of reach of children. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Rinse packaging before recycling. For advice, please contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26 or New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If in eyes, wash out with a large amount of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor.
